Release Date: 18 July 2025

Synopsis:
Yash Raj Films’ Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love story…and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple question…do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

Synopsis:
Yash Raj Films’ Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love story…and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple question…do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

snippet.title: Alcohol - Official Teaser | Allari Naresh, Ruhani Sharma, Niharika Nm  | Meher Tej | S Naga Vamsi
snippet.description:
Watch Alcohol - Official Teaser | Allari Naresh, Ruhani Sharma, Niharika Nm  | Meher Tej | S Naga Vamsi 

Alcohol is a Telugu feature film starring Allari Naresh, Ruhani Sharma, Niharika NM, Satya, and an ensemble cast. Directed by Meher Tej, the film features music by Ghibran, background score by Chaitan Bharadwaj, cinematography by Jiju Sunny, and editing by Niranjan Devaramane.

Produced by Suryadevara Naga Vamsi and Sai Soujanya under Sithara Entertainments and Fortune Four Cinemas, the film is presented by Srikara Studios.

Cast: Allari Naresh, Ruhani Sharma, Niharika NM, Satya, Girish Kulkarni, Harshavardhan, Chaitanya Krishna, Ravindra Vijay, Raghu Babu, Venkatesh Kakumanu, Kireeti, Hariteja, Surya Bhagavan Das, Flora Jacob

snippet.title: Jana Nayagan Trailer | Thalapathy Vijay | H Vinoth | Pooja Hegde | Anirudh | KVN
snippet.description:
Jana Nayagan Trailer | Thalapathy Vijay | H Vinoth | Pooja Hegde | Anirudh | KVN

❯❯ In this Concept trailer video I'm displaying visual commentary on how a film idea could look, The purpose of This Mashup / Fan-made / Concept trailer videos is to demonstrate and conceptualize specific or non-existing film ideas, compile and transform clips from previously existing productions to create a creatively unique vision and giving new meaning. I've transformed the original work by adding My own unique value such as added high-quality edits and special effects to create completely new, original movie trailers. These are derivative works as defined by the United States Copyright Act 17 U.S.C. § 101, and as such, may find protection from copyright claims under the doctrine of fair use.

❯❯ In this channel I'm creating Mashup / Fan-made / Concept trailer videos, involve collecting multiple pieces of film footage from one or multiple movies and editing them to create a new trailer. Trailer mashups are often created for a movie that does not exist now or to change the genre of an existing film. These are derivative works and as such, may find protection from copyright claims under the doctrine of fair use. The trailer mashups are not only a user-generated form of digital creativity but a way to create anticipation for future releases, working in tandem with current movie trailers. Movie trailers are designed to give minimal plot detail and to create hype and anticipation. Fan-made trailer mashups allow the audience to perform their own cinematic spin on current movie footage. This allows the trailer to focus on a specific actor or portion of the film. It could even change the plot or genre of the film entirely.

snippet.title: Ram Jaane (Music Video) Anu Malik | Shahrukh Khan, Juhi Chawla | Alka Yagnik, Sonu Nigam|Hindi song
snippet.description:
“Ram Jaane” is the bold and unforgettable title track from the 1995 Bollywood action-drama Ram Jaane, sung by Udit Narayan, Alka Yagnik, Sonu Nigam and composed by Anu Malik. The song captures the gritty, rebellious spirit of the film’s lead character, played by Shah Rukh Khan, whose very name — Ram Jaane (meaning “God knows”) — becomes a powerful identity statement.

snippet.title: Bijuria | Sunny Sanskari Ki Tulsi Kumari | Varun, Janhvi,Sanya, Rohit | Sonu, Tanishk, Ravi, Asees
snippet.description:
Thirchhi nigahe mere dil pe giraye re bijuria, bijuria ⚡

A firecracker of a song 🧨, presenting ‘Bijuria’ from ‘Sunny Sanskari Ki Tulsi Kumari’! Featuring Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor, Rohit Saraf and Sanya Malhotra in the video, the song is composed by Tanishk Bagchi and Ravi Pawar. Sung by Sonu Nigam and Asees Kaur and penned by Sonu Nigam and Tanishk Bagchi, hit play, turn it up, and let the beat take over! 🔥🎧

#Bijuria #SunnySanskariKiTulsiKumari #VarunDhawan #JanhviKapoor #SonuNigam #TanishkBagchi 

🎵Stream Now: https://smi.lnk.to/Bijuria

Original music composer: Ravi Pawar 
New version reimagined by : Tanishk Bagchi
Singer: Sonu Nigam
Singer: Asees Kaur
Music Producer: Tanishk Bagchi
Original Lyrics by: Sonu Nigam & Ajay Jhingran
New Version Additional Lyrics by: Tanishk Bagchi
Tabla & Dholak: Raju Sardar, Sanjiv Sen, Sharafat, Arou
Female Chorus: Shudhi Ramani, Abhiruchi Singh, Megha Bhardwaj, Nikitha Venkatesh
Male Chorus: Vivek Naik, Rahul Chitnis, Sagar Lele, Santosh Bote
Chorus Recorded at: Input One
Recording Engineer: Sameer Dharap (Input One)
Chorus Recorded at: Studio 504
Recording Engineer: Rahul M Sharma (Studio 504)
Mix and Master Engineer: Eric Pillai @ Future Sounds of Bombay
Assistant Mix Engineer: Michael Edwin Pillai @ Future Sounds of Bombay
Special Thanks : Hero
Special Thanks: Sumeet Kr Tyagi
Music Supervisor: Azeem Dayani
Sr Associate Music Supervisor: Tanvi Asher
Jr Associate Music Supervisor: Vasundhara Misra
Music Team: Heer Kamdar
Additional Production  - Krishna Kishor 
Rhythm Performed - Krishna kishor, K V Prasad, Rahul

Dharma Productions & Mentor Disciple Entertainment present 
A Dharma Productions Film
Starring Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor, Sanya Malhotra, & Rohit Saraf
Directed by Shashank Khaitan
Produced by Hiroo Yash Johar, Karan Johar, Adar Poonawalla, Apoorva Mehta & Shashank Khaitan
Co-produced by Marijke deSouza 
Written by Shashank Khaitan
Dialogues by Shashank Khaitan & Ishita Moitra

Director Of Choreography: Piyush - Shazia
Song Editor: Rishabh Shetty 
Asst Editor: Hrushi

Releasing on 2nd October, 2025

Lyrics:

Bann jaye-gi, yeh bann jaye-gi, re teri dhulania (x2)

Tujhe lage na najariya,
Kyun na odhe tu chunariya
Oh tujhe lage na najariya, odh le chunariya

Thirchhi nigahe mere dil pe
Giraye re bijuria, bijuria

Bijuriaaaaa

Thirchhi nigahe mere dil pe
Giraye re bijuria, bijuria

(Music)
Haye tera sharmana, tauba tera itraana
Jo bhi dekhe ho jaye woh deewana tera

Sone jaisa tan tera, uff bhola pan tera
Mujko bhi kar gaya deewana tera

O sun baki re gujariya,
Yahi bole hai dagaria
Sun baki re gujariya, bole ye dagaria

Lachke kamariya toh chhalke
Gagariya ki luti re bajaria (x2)

(Music)

Ooo…lachke kamariya toh thirke bijuria
Bachke dagariya toh girke bijuria

Oore bijuria x 2

Naino se maare chori aisan bijuria…aaahhh

Oh mujhe lage na najariya,
Maine odhe li chunariya
mujhe lage na najariya,
odhe li chunariya,
Mera hi deewana mere
dil pe fida hai…
Banungi mein dhulaniya

Dhulaniaaaaa

Mera hi deewana mere
dil pe fida hai…
Banungi mein dhulaniya

Thirchhi nigahe mere dil pe
giraye re bijuria, bijuria (x2)

(Music)

Lachke kamariya toh
Bachke dagariya toh

Ohh ohh re bijuria
Naino se maare chori aisan bijuria…

Aaahhh…aaah…aaaaa!!

snippet.title: Saiyaara (1980) Ft. Kishore Kumar full song (Old version) Old is Gold with a New Voice!
snippet.description:
Saiyaara (1980) Ft. Kishore Kumar full song (Old version) Old is Gold with a New Voice!

The full version is finally here! We converted the vocals sung amazingly by RJ Kisna into kishore da's voice using AI, and I produced the retro background music, let me know if ya'll want a breakdown of how I do these retro versions! 




🌍 Follow me here for more fun and behind the scenes:
Instagram - 
@anshuman.sharma1 |   / anshuman.sharma1  
Twitter - @anshumonsharma |   / anshumonsharma  
Facebook - @anshuman.sharma111 |   / anshuman.sharma1  

Saiyaara (1980) – Kishore Kumar's Saiyaara Full Song 
Step back in time and relive the golden era of Bollywood with Kishore Kumar's rare gem "Saiyaara" (1980). This soulful melody captures the essence of vintage romance, timeless lyrics, and the golden voice of Kishore Da that still resonates in every heart.

Whether you're a lifelong Kishore fan or discovering his magic for the first time, this song is a journey into the past that you don't want to mi

Credit goes to _Rakesh Sutradhar 🙏

[Verse 1]
Tu paas hai mere paas hai aise
Mera koi ehsaas hai jaise

Tu paas hai mere paas hai aise
Mera koi ehsaas hai jaise

Haaye main mar hi jaaun
Jo tujhko na paaun
Baaton mein teri main raatein bitaaun

Honthon pe lamha lamha
Hai naam tera haaye
Tujhko hi gaaun main, tujhko pukaaroon

[Chorus]
Saiyaara tu toh badla nahin hai
Mausam zara sa rootha hua hai

Saiyaara tu toh badla nahin hai
Mausam zara sa rootha hua hai

[Verse 2]
Beetey lamhon se duniya basa loon
Main toh tere aansuon ka bana hoon

Meri hansi mein teri sadaayein
Teri kahaani khud ko sunaaun

Yaadon ke taare, yaadon ke taare tootenge kaise
Mere hain jo woh roothenge kaise

Beetey dinon ki kholi kitaabein
Guzre palon ko kaise bhula dein

Haaye main mar hi jaaun
Jo tujhko na paaun
Baaton mein teri main raatein bitaaun

Honthon pe lamha lamha
Hai naam tera haaye
Tujhko hi gaaun main, tujhko pukaaroon

[Chorus Repeat]
Saiyaara tu toh badla nahin hai
Mausam zara sa rootha hua hai

Saiyaara tu toh badla nahin hai
Mausam zara sa rootha hua hai

[Bridge]
Jis roz hum tum phir se milenge
Yeh saari baatein tujhse kahenge

Duniya mein chaahe ban jaayein jo bhi
Tere bina tab kuch na rahenge

[Outro]
Haaye main mar hi jaaun
Jo tujhko na paaun
Jo tujhko na paaun
Main mar hi jaaun

Honthon pe lamha lamha
Hai naam tera haaye
Tujhko hi gaaun main, tujhko pukaaroon



👇 Let us know your favorite Kishore Kumar song in the comments! 👇
💬 What memories does this song bring back for you?

snippet.title: धीमी आवाज मे गर्भवती 9 महीने तक सुने गर्भ भजन, होगी पुत्र प्राप्ति #pregnancybhajan #garbhraksha
snippet.description:
⭐RT : 2455
⭐SONG:  Jai Jai Radha Raman 
⭐SINGER : Bal krishan (Anoop Sharma)
⭐MUSIC : RT Beats
⭐PRODUCER: Mukesh Nandal
⭐DIRECTOR: Om Veer Singh 
⭐MUSIC LABEL: Garbh Raksha
⭐PARENT LABEL: Realtime Production 7206682860
⭐CATEGORY: Hindi Devotional ( Bhajan)

🌼 "Jai Jai Radha Raman" एक अत्यंत मधुर और शांतिपूर्ण कृष्ण भजन है, जिसे विशेष रूप से गर्भवती महिलाओं के मानसिक और आत्मिक स्वास्थ्य के लिए प्रस्तुत किया गया है। यह भजन माँ के हृदय को भक्ति से भर देता है और गर्भस्थ शिशु के लिए एक सकारात्मक ऊर्जा का संचार करता है।

🕉️ भजन का सार:
“राधा रमण” यानी श्रीकृष्ण जो राधा के प्रियतम हैं। इस भजन में हम भगवान कृष्ण की आराधना करते हैं, जो प्रेम, करुणा और सौंदर्य के प्रतीक हैं। यह भजन माँ और गर्भस्थ शिशु के बीच एक दिव्य संबंध स्थापित करता है।

गर्भावस्था के समय जब मन अस्थिर होता है, शरीर थकता है और चिंता घर कर लेती है — तब श्रीकृष्ण के भजन शांति और ऊर्जा का संचार करते हैं।

🌸 गर्भवती महिलाओं के लिए लाभ:
तनाव और चिंता में कमी: भजन सुनने से हार्मोनल संतुलन बेहतर होता है

शिशु के मस्तिष्क पर सकारात्मक प्रभाव: गर्भ में सुनी गई ध्वनियाँ बच्चे के मस्तिष्क के विकास में सहायक होती हैं

माँ और शिशु का आध्यात्मिक जुड़ाव

मन में विश्वास और ऊर्जा का संचार

नींद में सुधार और मानसिक शांति

🧘‍♀️ कैसे और कब सुनें यह भजन?
सुबह-सुबह ध्यान के समय

रात को सोने से पहले

प्रेगनेंसी योग या गार्भिक ध्यान करते समय

जब भी आप मानसिक रूप से थकी हों या असहज महसूस करें

💫 "Jai Jai Radha Raman" का भावार्थ:
“हे राधा रमण! मुझे शक्ति दो, मुझे धैर्य दो, ताकि मैं इस मातृत्व की यात्रा को शांतिपूर्वक और प्रेमपूर्वक पूरी कर सकूं।
मेरा शिशु भी तुम्हारी तरह कोमल, शांत और करुणामयी बने।”

Jai Jai Radha Raman Krishna Bhajan

snippet.description:
🌺🙏जय श्री हरि विष्णु🙏🌺


⭐Start your day with "Bhajan" to bring peace to your soul.
⭐ मन की शांति के लिए " Vishnu Aradhna " यूट्यूब चैनल पर भजन और भक्ति गीत,आरती,चालीसा व मंत्र सुने ⭐ Please subscribe to the channel and press Bell icon for all the updates, we are coming up with many new Bhajans  💗﻿🌸


इस जीवन में ना तो कुछ खोता है और ना ही कुछ व्यर्थ होता है प्रभु श्री हरि विष्णु जी के भक्ति भजनों अथवा कथाओं से अपने हृदय को स्वच्छ कर श्री हरि विष्णु जी के भक्ति भजनों एवं कथाओं का आनंद लें और सर्वाधिक कथा भजनों के बोलों से कुछ सीख लें 🙏🙏        🌷🌷धन्यवाद🌷🌷

********                          **********************************            ************
                                         🌺ॐ नमः भगवते वासुदेवायः नमः🌺 


***************************************************************************
पूर्णिमा के दिन नारायण कवच सुनने मात्र से अखंड सौभाग्य की प्राप्ति होगी#VishnuNarayankawach
***************************************************************************
shriman narayana stotram,srimannarayana hari hari song,vishnu sahasranama stotram,shriman narayan kirtan,vishnu sahasranamam,laxmi narayan mantra 108 times,vishnu sahasranamam fast,srimannarayana song,narayana upanishad,on namo bhagavate vasudevaya mantra,narayan kavas

vishnu bhagwan ki aarti,vishnu bhagwan ki katha aur aarti,vishnu bhagwan ki katha,विष्णु भगवान का मंत्र,विष्णु सॉन्ग,विशु

🙏 Title - Narayan Kawach
🙏 Singer - Jyoti Tiwari
🙏 Music -Prabhu Kripa Studio
🙏 Lyrics - Traditional"Raj Anari"
🙏 Edit - DIGINOR TEAM
🙏 Label - Vishnu Aradhna 
🙏 Copyright - DIGINOR 



विष्णु जी की लीलाओं अथवा कथा,भजन,मीठे भजनों को सुनाने के इच्छुक हो और भगवान विष्णु जी के प्रिय दिन (बृहस्पतिवार) को विष्णु जी के कथा भजनों का आनंद लेना चाहते हो तो हमारे चेंनल #VIshnu Aradhna को ज्यादा से ज्यादा सब्सक्राइब करें | 
                                                         और
ऐसे ही प्रभु भक्ति में लीन होकर कथा भजनों को अपने परिवार जनो के साथ मिलकर ज्यादा से ज्यादा भक्ति भजनों का प्रचार प्रसार करें 


                                                          धन्यवाद

Mahre Hote Haath Gerde Mahara Jeen Ka Fayda Ke ..
Re 
Unki Teere Laash Naale Mei 
Beshak Karde Fon Saale Nei
Jindgi Di Uppar Aale Nei
Jeeke Suthri Dhaal Mariye... 

Jyukar Duryodhan Ki Khatar 
Ran Mei Karan Khada Tha Aadke 
Nyue Teri Khatar Khada yaar Tera
Chinta na kariye …
Re Saamhi Arjun Ho Ya Koi Uste Bhi Bada Yodha Je Na Mila Khaak Mei Aaya Mere Te Fer Baat Kariye ..

Jo Asal Mard Mei Khubi Wo Mahare Saari Pawengi 
Ghaate Mei Khoon Ho Chae Na Howe Par Khudari Pawegi..
Amar Mei Nu Toh Bojh S Thoda Par Baat Bhari Pawegi... Karnawliya Lakh Bura Par Na Gadari Pawegi
Aare Hum Issi Baat Te Chaegye Jiste Lage To Bs Lagye Humto Yaari Tod Nibhaya Gaye Tu Bi Baat Te Na Firye

Jyukar Duryodhan Ki Khatar 
Ran Mei Karan Khada Tha Aadke 
Nyue Teri Khatar Khada yaar Tera
Chinta na kariye
Re Saamhi Arjun Ho Ya Koi Uste Bhi Bada Yodha Je Na Mila Khaak Mei Aaya Mere Te Fer Baat Kariye
